{"tid":1107353,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹日記","createTime":"2019-04-15T07:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T14:54:31.000Z","uid":222576,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"00bed3bd8ec87a9b109175efcf6568d523a01e4b","tid":1107353,"uid":222576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:48:47.000Z","msg":"一直以黎濕疹時好時壞，但係一搽類固醇就好，所以都少理。上年5月去左大陸實習一個月，再去英國讀書一個月，果兩個月食嘢毫無節制，有幾油就幾油，幾唔健康就幾唔健康，海鮮牛炸野零食酒咩都齊，果時見皮膚無咩反應就以為自己唔再敏感。結果翻到香港大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 塊面個身周圍都係，又紅又鞋，又返翻中學dse果時極嚴重狀態。<br />\n<br />\n於是我的起心肝由11月開始戒類固醇，飲食變返清淡戒翻口，睇翻中醫，食supplements，但係都好得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紅既情況少左，但係個身好乾燥。返學被逼出街既時候搽幾多層都無用，真係覺得自己好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我決定今日開始完全戒清， 以此post紀錄我既飲食，希望有改善。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNeD43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNeD43.png&h=d3fd4069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早餐：米奶 <br />\n午餐：菜，肉，飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> + 甜品：中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7461681dd2866bb0a7cd97cfccc9d275a080872","tid":1107353,"uid":222576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tz3tKHE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftz3tKHE.png&h=146ace7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晚餐： 菜 肉 飯 + 一舊細蕃薯（想食甜嘢） + 中藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24eb5cc7a85fb31ddedf4d6fd6e14b42ed19026","tid":1107353,"uid":157369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:24:22.000Z","msg":"所以有冇諗過係「香港」問題<br />\n利申：去外國手腳鼻敏感都冇發過"},{"pid":"680ffea058a793b3d5b1e499b3174b61f6adc6ea","tid":1107353,"uid":222576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d24eb5cc7a85fb31ddedf4d6fd6e14b42ed19026","tid":1107353,"uid"